{"tid":2361812,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"是靚午 口水雞扒飯","createTime":"2021-01-11T04:09:23.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T15:12:04.000Z","uid":33359,"like":119,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"49d7a5eabcec5509571ad1356d05a4b9227183dd","tid":2361812,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:09:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bjjPVG2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbjjPVG2.jpg&h=7f6bd6a8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0n7U6OK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0n7U6OK.jpg&h=7314687d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講吓味道先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢間既口水汁係我係觀塘食過最好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咸香鮮麻辣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全部都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個汁真係有一粒粒花椒粒係入面<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞扒都整得嫩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雞皮夠爽脆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有啲青瓜底清一清味蕾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n食落條脷根好c伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026a5a21e88c9f439d440fc06ced685c5339605b","tid":2361812,"uid":78039,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:10:02.000Z","msg":"邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23846c6a8b59d1529329f2be33eb83baa5839c74","tid":2361812,"uid":6225,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T04:10:16.000Z","msg":"口水師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji